&nbsp;

<h3>Fedora</h3>

Official Fedora builds can be found <a href="https://admin.fedoraproject.org/updates/sparkleshare">here</a>.

&nbsp;

<h3>Ubuntu</h3>

Official Ubuntu builds can be found in <a href="https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/sparkleshare">Launchpad</a>.

&nbsp;

<h3>Source</h3>

Get the source code <a href="https://github.com/hbons/SparkleShare/downloads">here</a>.

Compiling and installing from source is pretty straightforward. The README has a list of dependencies and instructions on how to install them with one command on the most popular distros.

&nbsp;
<h3>Snow Leopard &amp; Lion</h3>
The latest bundle can be found <a href="https://github.com/hbons/SparkleShare/downloads">on Github</a> under <em>Download Packages</em>.
